                </section>
                <section class="mp-settings-section is-wide">
                    <div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>Event check-in scanner</h4><p>Each event has its own protected public scanner link. Configure how quickly a result closes before the next ticket can be scanned.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="row"><div class="col-md-5 form-group mb-0"><label asp-for="ScannerResultSeconds" class="form-label">Result auto-close (seconds)</label><input asp-for="ScannerResultSeconds" type="number" min="0" max="60" step="1" class="form-control"><span asp-validation-for="ScannerResultSeconds" class="text-danger"></span><div class="form-text">Set to 0 to keep each result open until staff selects “Close · scan next”. Default: 5 seconds.</div></div></div>
                    <div class="mp-settings-note mt-3"><strong>Privacy-safe by design.</strong> Scanner pages are event-scoped, excluded from search and analytics, and exchange their protected link into an HttpOnly staff session before scanning begins.</div>
                </section>
            </div></div>
        </section>

        <section class="mp-settings-panel" id="settings-panel-analytics" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="settings-tab-analytics" data-settings-panel="analytics" hidden>
            <header class="mp-settings-panel-head"><div><h3>Analytics &amp; ecommerce events</h3><p>Connect one Google provider and control privacy behavior without exposing attendee or payment data.</p></div></header>
            <div class="mp-settings-panel-body"><div class="mp-settings-grid">
                <section class="mp-settings-section">
                    <div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>Connection</h4><p>Choose GTM or direct GA4 to avoid duplicate reporting.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="form-group"><label asp-for="AnalyticsProvider" class="form-label">Analytics provider</label><select asp-for="AnalyticsProvider" asp-items="Html.GetEnumSelectList<AnalyticsProvider>()" class="form-select" data-analytics-provider></select><div class="form-text">Disabled keeps the local <code>dataLayer</code> event contract available.</div></div>
                    <div class="form-group" data-analytics-field="gtm"><label asp-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="form-label">GTM container ID</label><input asp-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="form-control font-monospace" placeholder="GTM-ABC123" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"><span asp-validation-for="GoogleTagManagerContainerId" class="text-danger"></span></div>
                    <div class="form-group" data-analytics-field="ga4"><label asp-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="form-label">GA4 measurement ID</label><input asp-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="form-control font-monospace" placeholder="G-ABC123DEF4" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false"><span asp-validation-for="GoogleAnalyticsMeasurementId" class="text-danger"></span></div>
                </section>
                <section class="mp-settings-section">
                    <div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>Privacy &amp; event contract</h4><p>Control script loading and review the normalized events available to your analytics workspace.</p></div></div>
                    <div class="form-check mb-2"><input asp-for="RequireAnalyticsConsent" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="RequireAnalyticsConsent" class="form-check-label">Require visitor consent before loading Google scripts</label></div>
                    <div class="form-check mb-3"><input asp-for="RespectDoNotTrack" class="form-check-input"><label asp-for="RespectDoNotTrack" class="form-check-label">Respect browser Do Not Track</label></div>
                    <div class="mp-settings-note"><strong>Events included</strong><br><code>view_item_list</code>, <code>select_item</code>, <code>view_item</code>, <code>add_to_cart</code>, <code>remove_from_cart</code>, <code>view_cart</code>, <code>begin_checkout</code>, <code>add_payment_info</code>, and <code>purchase</code>. Payloads exclude buyer and attendee PII, access tokens, invoice IDs, payment addresses, and ticket codes.</div>
                </section>
            </div></div>
        </section>

        <section class="mp-settings-panel" id="settings-panel-domain" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="settings-tab-domain" data-settings-panel="domain" hidden>
            <header class="mp-settings-panel-head"><div><h3 id="ticket-domain-guide-title">Use your own domain</h3><p>Connect a dedicated hostname such as <code>tickets.yourdomain.com</code> and serve the store natively at <code>/events</code>.</p></div><span class="badge bg-info text-dark">Server administrator required</span></header>
            <div class="mp-settings-panel-body">
                <div class="mp-settings-grid">
                    <section class="mp-settings-section"><div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>Current public URL</h4><p>The canonical event URL used by this store.</p></div></div><a class="ticket-domain-url font-monospace" href="@canonicalPublicUrl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@canonicalPublicUrl</a></section>
                    <section class="mp-settings-section"><div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>Clean-domain URL</h4><p>Available after DNS, HTTPS, and native App mapping are configured.</p></div></div><code class="ticket-domain-url">@cleanPublicExample</code></section>
                    <section class="mp-settings-section is-wide">
                        <div class="alert alert-info"><strong>Native clean routes are available.</strong> Once enabled, every ticket directory, event, cart, attendee form, payment status, confirmation, PDF, rebuy, and Apple Wallet link uses <code>https://&lt;host&gt;/events/…</code>. Existing <code>/stores/@storeId/events/…</code> links continue to work and their GET/HEAD requests move to the clean hostname; POST requests are never cross-host redirected.</div>
                        <div class="mp-settings-section-head"><div><h4>BTCPay App domain mapping</h4><p>Create a native Event Tickets App explicitly, then map the dedicated hostname on BTCPay's server-level Policies page. Merely opening or saving this plugin never creates an App record.</p></div>@if(eventTicketsApps.Count==0 && createEventTicketsAppUrl is not null){<a class="btn btn-primary" href="@createEventTicketsAppUrl">Create Event Tickets App</a>}</div>
                        @if (domainMappingWarning is not null){<div class="alert alert-warning"><strong>Domain mapping inactive or ambiguous.</strong> @domainMappingWarning</div>}
                        @if(eventTicketsApps.Count==0){<div class="alert alert-info mb-3">No Event Tickets App exists for this store. Create one, give it a clear name, then return here. Creating the App does not publish or otherwise change the ticket shop.</div>}else{
                            <div class="list-group mb-3">@foreach(var app in eventTicketsApps){var isMapped=mappedDomain is not null && mappedEventTicketsApp?.Id==app.Id;<div class="list-group-item d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between align-items-center gap-2"><div><strong>@app.Name</strong><div class="small text-muted font-monospace">@app.Id</div></div>@if(isMapped){<span class="badge bg-success">Mapped to @mappedDomain</span>}else{<span class="badge bg-secondary">Not mapped</span>}</div>}</div>
                            @if(eventTicketsApps.Count>1){<div class="alert alert-warning">More than one Event Tickets App exists for this store. Keep one active identity and archive duplicates; the clean storefront follows the App selected by native domain mapping.</div>}
                        }
                        <dl class="row mb-3"><dt class="col-sm-3">Mapped hostname</dt><dd class="col-sm-9"><code>@(mappedDomain ?? "Not mapped")</code></dd><dt class="col-sm-3">Clean URL</dt><dd class="col-sm-9"><code>@cleanPublicExample</code></dd></dl>
                        @if(canManageServerDomains){<a class="btn btn-primary" asp-controller="UIServer" asp-action="Policies">Open Server Settings → Policies</a><div class="form-text mt-2">Under <strong>Domain to app mapping</strong>, add the exact canonical ASCII hostname and select the Event Tickets App above. BTCPay uses the first exact hostname row, so remove duplicate rows; later conflicting mappings are inactive.</div>}else{<div class="alert alert-secondary mb-0">Only a BTCPay server administrator can change the server-wide domain-to-App mapping. Ask an administrator to map the desired hostname to the exact App ID.</div>}
                    </section>
                </div>
                <details class="ticket-domain-step mt-3">
                    <summary>Server-owner checklist for a branded hostname</summary>
                    <ol class="mt-3 mb-2"><li>Create and verify the A/AAAA record, or a CNAME for a subdomain, so it resolves to the BTCPay server or external proxy.</li><li>Add the new hostname without removing existing entries from <code>BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS</code>, then rerun Docker setup as root.</li><li>Open <strong>Server Settings → Policies</strong> and map the exact canonical ASCII hostname to the Event Tickets App. Do not include whitespace, a trailing dot, scheme, port, or path.</li><li>Verify HTTPS, ticket selection, BTCPay checkout, status polling, PDF delivery, and wallet links.</li></ol>
                    <pre><code># Run from the btcpayserver-docker installation directory as root.
# Keep every hostname that is already configured.
export BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS="&lt;all-existing-additional-hosts&gt;,tickets.yourdomain.com"
. ./btcpay-setup.sh -i</code></pre>
                    <p class="small text-muted mt-2 mb-0">Do not add an unresolved hostname: a failed Let's Encrypt request can affect certificate renewal for other configured domains.</p>
                    <p class="small text-muted mt-2 mb-0"><code>BTCPAY_ADDITIONAL_HOSTS</code> aliases the whole BTCPay Server, not only this store. Other BTCPay routes remain reachable on that hostname.</p>
                </details>
                <p class="mt-3 mb-2"><strong>Use a dedicated subdomain when possible.</strong> If the apex domain already hosts a website, that website's reverse proxy or CDN must own the <code>/events</code> routing.</p>
                <div class="ticket-domain-links small"><a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/Docker/#environment-variables" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BTCPay Docker domain settings</a><a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/FAQ/Apps/#how-to-map-a-domain-name-to-an-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">How BTCPay maps domains to Apps</a><a href="https://docs.btcpayserver.org/FAQ/Deployment/#can-i-use-an-existing-nginx-server-as-a-reverse-proxy-with-ssl-termination" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">External reverse-proxy requirements</a></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div class="mp-settings-savebar">
            <p>Changes apply to every public event, checkout, payment, and ticket-delivery page after this form is saved.</p>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" data-settings-submit><svg class="mp-settings-icon" aria-hidden="true"><use href="@($"{iconSpriteUrl}#done")"></use></svg>Save settings</button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>

<script>
(()=>{
    const form=document.getElementById('ticket-settings-form');
    const tabs=Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-settings-tab]'));
    const panels=Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-settings-panel]'));
    if(!form||!tabs.length||!panels.length)return;
    const known=new Set(tabs.map(tab=>tab.dataset.settingsTab));
    const activate=(key,{focus=false,updateHash=false}={})=>{
        if(!known.has(key))key='storefront';
        tabs.forEach(tab=>{const active=tab.dataset.settingsTab===key;tab.setAttribute('aria-selected',String(active));tab.tabIndex=active?0:-1});
        panels.forEach(panel=>{const active=panel.dataset.settingsPanel===key;panel.hidden=!active;panel.classList.toggle('is-active',active)});
        try{sessionStorage.setItem('makepay:event-ticket-settings:@storeId',key)}catch{}
        if(updateHash)history.replaceState(null,'',location.pathname+location.search+'#settings-'+key);
        if(focus)tabs.find(tab=>tab.dataset.settingsTab===key)?.focus({preventScroll:true});
    };
    const invalid=form.querySelector('.input-validation-error,[aria-invalid="true"],.field-validation-error,[data-upload-invalid="true"]');
    const invalidPanel=invalid?.closest('[data-settings-panel]')?.dataset.settingsPanel;
    const hashKey=location.hash.startsWith('#settings-')?location.hash.slice(10):'';
    let stored='';
    try{stored=sessionStorage.getItem('makepay:event-ticket-settings:@storeId')||''}catch{}
    activate(invalidPanel||hashKey||stored||'storefront');
    if(invalidPanel)document.querySelector('.mp-settings-validation')?.focus({preventScroll:true});
    tabs.forEach((tab,index)=>{
        tab.addEventListener('click',()=>activate(tab.dataset.settingsTab,{updateHash:true}));
        tab.addEventListener('keydown',event=>{
            let next=index;
            if(event.key==='ArrowRight')next=(index+1)%tabs.length;
            else if(event.key==='ArrowLeft')next=(index-1+tabs.length)%tabs.length;
            else if(event.key==='Home')next=0;
            else if(event.key==='End')next=tabs.length-1;
            else return;
            event.preventDefault();
            activate(tabs[next].dataset.settingsTab,{focus:true,updateHash:true});
        });
    });
    form.addEventListener('invalid',event=>{
        const panel=event.target.closest('[data-settings-panel]')?.dataset.settingsPanel;
        if(panel)activate(panel,{updateHash:true});
    },true);
    document.querySelectorAll('[data-open-theme-editor]').forEach(button=>button.addEventListener('click',()=>document.getElementById('open-theme-editor')?.click()));
    form.addEventListener('submit',event=>{if(form.dataset.submitting==='true'){event.preventDefault();return}form.dataset.submitting='true';form.setAttribute('aria-busy','true');form.querySelectorAll('[data-settings-submit]').forEach(button=>button.disabled=true);document.querySelectorAll('[data-settings-submit][form="ticket-settings-form"]').forEach(button=>button.disabled=true)});
    addEventListener('pageshow',()=>{delete form.dataset.submitting;form.removeAttribute('aria-busy');document.querySelectorAll('[data-settings-submit]').forEach(button=>button.disabled=false)});
})();
</script>
<dialog class="theme-editor-dialog" id="theme-editor" aria-label="Live ticket page editor">
    <div class="theme-editor-shell">
        <header class="theme-editor-header"><div><strong>Live ticket experience editor</strong><div class="small text-muted">Changes appear instantly and save with the settings form.</div></div><div class="theme-editor-header-actions"><button type="button" id="close-theme-editor">Close</button><button type="button" class="primary" id="save-theme-editor">Save design</button></div></header>
        <div class="theme-editor-body">
            <aside class="theme-editor-controls">
                <h3>Brand</h3>
                <label for="editor-StorefrontTitle">Storefront name</label><input id="editor-StorefrontTitle" data-editor-target="StorefrontTitle">
                <label for="editor-LogoUrl">Logo URL</label><input id="editor-LogoUrl" data-editor-target="LogoUrl">
                <label for="editor-FaviconUrl">Browser favicon URL</label><input id="editor-FaviconUrl" data-editor-target="FaviconUrl" type="url" placeholder="https://example.com/favicon.png">
                <label for="editor-HeroImageUrl">Hero image URL</label><input id="editor-HeroImageUrl" data-editor-target="HeroImageUrl">
                <label for="editor-HeroHeadline">Headline</label><textarea id="editor-HeroHeadline" data-editor-target="HeroHeadline" rows="2"></textarea>
                <label for="editor-HeroSubheadline">Supporting copy</label><textarea id="editor-HeroSubheadline" data-editor-target="HeroSubheadline" rows="2"></textarea>
                <h3>Checkout copy</h3>
                <label for="editor-TicketPageTitle">Ticket page title</label><input id="editor-TicketPageTitle" data-editor-target="TicketPageTitle">
                <label for="editor-TicketPageSubtitle">Ticket page subtitle</label><textarea id="editor-TicketPageSubtitle" data-editor-target="TicketPageSubtitle" rows="2"></textarea>
                <label for="editor-ConfirmationTitle">Confirmation title</label><input id="editor-ConfirmationTitle" data-editor-target="ConfirmationTitle">
                <label for="editor-ConfirmationMessage">Confirmation message</label><textarea id="editor-ConfirmationMessage" data-editor-target="ConfirmationMessage" rows="2"></textarea>
                <h3>Layout &amp; colors</h3>
                <label for="editor-FontStyle">Typeface style</label><select id="editor-FontStyle" data-editor-target="FontStyle"><option value="0">System sans</option><option value="1">Modern sans</option><option value="2">Rounded sans</option><option value="3">Editorial serif</option><option value="4">Neo-grotesk sans</option></select>
                <label for="editor-BrandPanelWidth">Hero width</label><input id="editor-BrandPanelWidth" data-editor-target="BrandPanelWidth" type="range" min="35" max="60">
                <div class="theme-editor-color-grid">
                    <div><label for="editor-AccentColor">Accent</label><input id="editor-AccentColor" data-editor-target="AccentColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-AccentTextColor">Button text</label><input id="editor-AccentTextColor" data-editor-target="AccentTextColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-BrandTextColor">Hero text</label><input id="editor-BrandTextColor" data-editor-target="BrandTextColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-PageBackgroundColor">Page</label><input id="editor-PageBackgroundColor" data-editor-target="PageBackgroundColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-SurfaceColor">Cards</label><input id="editor-SurfaceColor" data-editor-target="SurfaceColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-TextColor">Text</label><input id="editor-TextColor" data-editor-target="TextColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-TimerColor">Timer</label><input id="editor-TimerColor" data-editor-target="TimerColor" type="color"></div>
                    <div><label for="editor-TimerTextColor">Timer text</label><input id="editor-TimerTextColor" data-editor-target="TimerTextColor" type="color"></div>
                </div>
            </aside>
            <section class="theme-editor-preview">
                <div class="theme-editor-toolbar"><div class="theme-editor-state"><button type="button" data-preview-state="tickets" class="is-active">Tickets</button><button type="button" data-preview-state="cart">Cart</button><button type="button" data-preview-state="checkout">Checkout</button><button type="button" data-preview-state="payment">Payment</button><button type="button" data-preview-state="success">Success</button></div><div><button type="button" data-preview-device="desktop" class="is-active">Desktop</button> <button type="button" data-preview-device="mobile">Mobile</button></div></div>
                <div class="theme-editor-canvas"><div class="theme-editor-frame-wrap"><iframe class="theme-editor-frame" id="theme-editor-frame" sandbox="allow-same-origin" title="Ticket page preview"></iframe></div></div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</dialog>
<script>
(()=>{const dialog=document.getElementById('theme-editor'),form=document.getElementById('ticket-settings-form'),frame=document.getElementById('theme-editor-frame'),wrap=frame.closest('.theme-editor-frame-wrap'),editorFields=[...dialog.querySelectorAll('[data-editor-target]')],btcpayLogo=@Html.Raw(System.Text.Json.JsonSerializer.Serialize(btcpayLogoUrl));let state='tickets',previewScroll=0;frame.addEventListener('load',()=>{try{frame.contentWindow?.scrollTo(0,previewScroll)}catch{}});
const source=id=>document.getElementById(id),value=id=>source(id)?.value||'',escapeHtml=text=>String(text||'').replace(/[&<>"]/g,char=>({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;'}[char])),color=(id,fallback)=>/^#[0-9a-f]{6}$/i.test(value(id))?value(id):fallback,url=id=>{try{const parsed=new URL(value(id));return /^https?:$/.test(parsed.protocol)?parsed.href:''}catch{return''}};
const syncFromForm=()=>editorFields.forEach(field=>{const target=source(field.dataset.editorTarget);if(target)field.value=target.value});
const font=()=>({0:"system-ui,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',sans-serif",1:"'Helvetica Neue',Inter,system-ui,-apple-system,'Segoe UI',sans-serif",2:"ui-rounded,'Arial Rounded MT Bold',system-ui,sans-serif",3:"Georgia,'Times New Roman',serif",4:"Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"}[value('FontStyle')]||"'Helvetica Neue',Inter,system-ui,sans-serif");
const stepper=step=>`<div class="steps"><b>STEP ${step} OF 4</b><div><span class="done">✓ Tickets</span><span class="${step===2?'now':step>2?'done':''}">2 Cart</span><span class="${step===3?'now':step>3?'done':''}">3 Checkout</span><span class="${step===4?'now':''}">4 Payment</span></div></div>`;
const shell=body=>`<div class="timer">14:42 &nbsp; Left to secure your tickets</div><main class="flow">${body}</main>`;
const render=()=>{const accent=color('AccentColor','#155eef'),accentText=color('AccentTextColor','#fff'),brandText=color('BrandTextColor','#fff'),page=color('PageBackgroundColor','#fff'),surface=color('SurfaceColor','#fff'),text=color('TextColor','#101828'),timer=color('TimerColor','#fec84b'),timerText=color('TimerTextColor','#101828'),image=url('HeroImageUrl'),logo=url('LogoUrl'),favicon=url('FaviconUrl'),title=escapeHtml(value('StorefrontTitle')),headline=escapeHtml(value('HeroHeadline')),sub=escapeHtml(value('HeroSubheadline')),pageTitle=escapeHtml(value('TicketPageTitle')),pageSubtitle=escapeHtml(value('TicketPageSubtitle')),confirmTitle=escapeHtml(value('ConfirmationTitle')),confirmMessage=escapeHtml(value('ConfirmationMessage'));
const css=`*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;background:${page};color:${text};font:15px/1.45 ${font()}}button{font:inherit}.split{display:grid;grid-template-columns:${Number(value('BrandPanelWidth'))||50}% 1fr;min-height:100vh}.brand{position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:${accent};color:${brandText};padding:50px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end}.brand>img.hero{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:.55}.brand-content{position:relative}.logo{max-height:45px;max-width:180px;margin-bottom:30px}.wordmark{font-weight:900;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:30px}.eyebrow{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:900}.brand h1{font-size:56px;line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.05em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:10px 0;max-width:10ch}.brand p{max-width:36em}.selector{padding:54px 42px}.selector h2{font-size:32px;line-height:1;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0}.muted{color:#667085}.table-head,.ticket{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 110px 110px;gap:18px}.table-head{border-bottom:2px solid #d0d5dd;padding:30px 0 10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:900}.ticket{padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e4e7ec}.ticket h3{margin:0 0 6px}.qty{display:flex;gap:7px;align-items:start}.qty span{border:1px solid #d0d5dd;border-radius:8px;padding:5px 10px}.primary{background:${accent};color:${accentText};border:0;border-radius:9px;padding:13px 20px;font-weight:900}.full{width:100%;margin-top:24px}.timer{height:48px;background:${timer};color:${timerText};display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:900}.flow{max-width:950px;margin:auto;padding:48px 24px}.steps{text-align:center;color:#98a2b3;font-size:12px;font-weight:800}.steps>div{display:flex;gap:28px;justify-content:center;margin:20px 0 38px}.steps span{padding:8px}.steps .done,.steps .now{color:${accent}}.steps .now{outline:2px solid ${accent};border-radius:999px}.card{border:1px solid #e4e7ec;border-radius:14px;background:${surface};overflow:hidden;margin-top:20px}.row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 120px 70px 110px;gap:15px;padding:16px 20px;border-top:1px solid #e4e7ec}.row.head{background:#f8fafc;border:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:900}.summary{background:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e4e7ec;border-radius:14px;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:20px}.summary div{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin:7px}.form-card{border:1px solid #e4e7ec;border-radius:14px;padding:22px;margin:20px 0}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:15px}.field label{display:block;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:5px}.field div{height:42px;border:1px solid #d0d5dd;border-radius:8px;background:${surface}}.attendee{border:6px solid ${accent};border-radius:14px;padding:16px;margin-top:20px}.pay{max-width:620px;margin:25px auto;border:1px solid #e4e7ec;border-radius:16px;background:${surface};padding:30px;text-align:center}.btcpay{height:320px;border:1px solid #d0d5dd;border-radius:12px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:#fff;color:#101828}.success{max-width:760px;margin:auto;padding:70px 24px}.success-mark{width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;background:#dcfae6;color:#067647;font-size:30px}.success h1{font-size:54px;letter-spacing:-.04em;margin:20px 0 8px}.pass{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 180px;gap:20px;border:1px solid #e4e7ec;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;margin-top:24px}.ticket-code{background:#f8fafc;border-radius:8px;padding:10px;font-family:monospace}.qr-space{border:1px solid #d0d5dd;border-radius:12px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:#667085}@@media(max-width:600px){.split{display:block}.brand{min-height:330px;padding:28px}.brand h1{font-size:38px}.selector{padding:34px 20px}.table-head{display:none}.ticket{grid-template-columns:1fr auto}.ticket .qty{grid-column:1/-1}.flow{padding:30px 16px}.steps span{font-size:0}.steps span::first-letter{font-size:12px}.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.row{grid-template-columns:1fr 45px 75px}.row span:nth-child(2){display:none}.pass{grid-template-columns:1fr}.success h1{font-size:40px}}`;
let body;if(state==='tickets'){body=`<div class="split"><aside class="brand">${image?`<img class="hero" src="${escapeHtml(image)}" alt="">`:''}<div class="brand-content">${logo?`<img class="logo" src="${escapeHtml(logo)}" alt="">`:`<div class="wordmark">${title}</div>`}<h1>${headline}</h1><p>${sub}</p><b>15 AUG 2026 · DUBAI</b></div></aside><section class="selector"><div class="eyebrow">BUILDER SUMMIT 2026</div><h2>${pageTitle}</h2><p class="muted">${pageSubtitle}</p><div class="table-head"><span>Ticket</span><span>Price</span><span>Quantity</span></div><div class="ticket"><div><h3>General admission</h3><span class="muted">Full-day summit access and community sessions.</span></div><b>25 USD</b><div class="qty"><span>−</span><b>1</b><span>+</span></div></div><div class="ticket"><div><h3>Builder VIP</h3><span class="muted">Reserved seating and speaker reception.</span></div><b>75 USD</b><div class="qty"><span>−</span><b>0</b><span>+</span></div></div><button class="primary full">CONTINUE · 25 USD</button></section></div>`}else if(state==='cart'){body=shell(`${stepper(2)}<h1>Review your cart</h1><p class="muted">Your selection is reserved while the timer is running.</p><div class="card"><div class="row head"><span>TICKET</span><span>PRICE</span><span>QTY</span><span>TOTAL</span></div><div class="row"><b>General admission</b><span>25 USD</span><span>1</span><b>25 USD</b></div></div><div class="summary"><div><span>Subtotal</span><b>25 USD</b></div><div><strong>Total</strong><strong>25 USD</strong></div></div><button class="primary full">CONTINUE</button>`)}else if(state==='checkout'){body=shell(`${stepper(3)}<h1>Billing details</h1><p class="muted">We use this information for your receipt and ticket delivery.</p><div class="form-card grid">${['First name','Last name','Email','Phone number'].map(label=>`<div class="field"><label>${label}</label><div></div></div>`).join('')}</div><h2>Attendee details</h2><div class="attendee"><b style="color:${accent}">GENERAL ADMISSION · ATTENDEE 1</b><div class="form-card grid">${['First name','Last name','Nickname','Email'].map(label=>`<div class="field"><label>${label}</label><div></div></div>`).join('')}</div></div><button class="primary full">PROCEED TO PAYMENT</button>`)}else if(state==='payment'){body=shell(`${stepper(4)}<div class="pay"><h1>Complete your payment</h1><p class="muted">BTCPay is embedded securely below.</p><div class="btcpay"><div><b>BTCPay secure checkout</b><p>Invoice preview</p><button class="primary">Choose payment method</button></div></div></div>`)}else{body=`<main class="success"><div class="success-mark">✓</div><div class="eyebrow">PAYMENT CONFIRMED</div><h1>${confirmTitle}</h1><p class="muted">${confirmMessage}</p><button class="primary">DOWNLOAD ALL TICKETS AS PDF</button><div class="pass"><div><div class="eyebrow">GENERAL ADMISSION</div><h2>James Example</h2><p class="muted">15 August 2026 · Dubai Knowledge Park</p><div class="ticket-code">TKT-84AF-91CD-2026</div></div><div class="qr-space">Ticket QR</div></div></main>`}let previewHtml=`<!doctype html><head><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">${favicon?`<link rel="icon" href="${escapeHtml(favicon)}">`:''}<style>${css}</style></head><body>${body}</body>`;if(state==='success')previewHtml=previewHtml.replace('grid-template-columns:1fr 180px;','grid-template-columns:1fr;').replace('<div class="success-mark">✓</div>','').replace('<div class="qr-space">Ticket QR</div>','');if(state==='payment')previewHtml=previewHtml.replace('<div class="btcpay"><div><b>BTCPay secure checkout</b><p>Invoice preview</p><button class="primary">Choose payment method</button></div></div>',`<div class="btcpay"><div><img src="${escapeHtml(btcpayLogo)}" alt="BTCPay Server" style="display:block;width:180px;max-width:70%;margin:0 auto 22px"><p>Secure modal checkout is ready.</p><button class="primary">Open secure checkout</button></div></div>`);frame.srcdoc=previewHtml};
let renderRequest=0;const scheduleRender=()=>{try{previewScroll=frame.contentWindow?.scrollY||0}catch{previewScroll=0}cancelAnimationFrame(renderRequest);renderRequest=requestAnimationFrame(render)};
editorFields.forEach(field=>field.addEventListener('input',()=>{const target=source(field.dataset.editorTarget);if(target){target.value=field.value;target.dispatchEvent(new Event('change',{bubbles:true}))}scheduleRender()}));
document.getElementById('open-theme-editor').addEventListener('click',()=>{syncFromForm();render();dialog.showModal()});document.getElementById('close-theme-editor').addEventListener('click',()=>dialog.close());document.getElementById('save-theme-editor').addEventListener('click',()=>{dialog.close();form.requestSubmit()});
dialog.querySelectorAll('[data-preview-state]').forEach(button=>button.addEventListener('click',()=>{dialog.querySelectorAll('[data-preview-state]').forEach(item=>item.classList.remove('is-active'));button.classList.add('is-active');state=button.dataset.previewState;render()}));dialog.querySelectorAll('[data-preview-device]').forEach(button=>button.addEventListener('click',()=>{dialog.querySelectorAll('[data-preview-device]').forEach(item=>item.classList.remove('is-active'));button.classList.add('is-active');wrap.classList.toggle('is-mobile',button.dataset.previewDevice==='mobile')}));})();
</script>
<script>
(()=>{const provider=document.querySelector('[data-analytics-provider]'),fields={gtm:document.querySelector('[data-analytics-field="gtm"]'),ga4:document.querySelector('[data-analytics-field="ga4"]')};if(!provider)return;const update=()=>{fields.gtm.hidden=provider.value!=='1';fields.ga4.hidden=provider.value!=='2'};provider.addEventListener('change',update);update()})();
</script>
